><p></p><p>Industrial Design World Expo has displayed the great achievements of industrial design in terms of industrial innovation, from consumption upgrading to high-end equipment, from smart city to IoT, from design-driven to industrial upgrades, from colleges and universities to the world&#39;s Top 500 enterprises, from independent designers to outstanding design companies, from information data to software systems, from industrial parks to innovation platform, from culture and arts to consumption upgrade, from venture capital investment to industrial incubation, from rural revitalization to poverty alleviation ... At the same time, it has demonstrated a major breakthrough in Chinese industrial design from the world&#39;s largest scale to a world-leading level. Industrial design has stepped on a new 100-year journey!</p><p><br/></p>";s:3:"eng";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:40:"/uploads/img1/20200416/5e982de9198d0.png";s:12:"picture_urls";s:65:"[{"url":"\/uploads\/img1\/20200113\/5e1bd52320a26.png","alt":""}]";s:10:"model_name";s:12:"单页模型";s:10:"table_name";s:4:"page";}i:33;a:22:{s:2:"id";s:2:"29";s:4:"name";s:24:"Sino-Italy Design Center";s:5:"ename";s:4:"sino";s:7:"cat_pic";s:40:"/uploads/img1/20200211/5e424bd0efad3.png";s:3:"pid";s:2:"17";s:8:"model_id";s:1:"2";s:4:"type";s:1:"0";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:24:"Sino-Italy Design Center";s:17:"template_category";s:0:"";s:13:"template_list";s:15:"List_foucs.html";s:13:"template_show";s:17:"Show_article.html";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:4:"sort";s:1:"2";s:3:"des";s:0:"";s:3:"eng";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:12:"picture_urls";s:2:"[]";s:10:"model_name";s:12:"单页模型";s:10:"table_name";s:4:"page";}i:34;a:22:{s:2:"id";s:2:"33";s:4:"name";s:23:"Alzheimer’s Apparatus";s:5:"ename";s:9:"Alzheimer";s:7:"cat_pic";s:40:"/uploads/img1/20200516/5ebf9cda568bc.jpg";s:3:"pid";s:2:"16";s:8:"model_id";s:1:"2";s:4:"type";s:1:"0";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description"