ment to upgrade to face the high-end and make greater contributions to the old and new growth driver replacement and the revitalization of the equipment manufacturing industry in China.</span></p><p style="margin: 0 0 10px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: Calibri;white-space: normal;line-height: 21px"><span style="font-size: 19px;line-height: 28px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">On Mathis Heller’s trip, Weichai highly recognized the results of the meeting between both parties and hope <a name="OLE_LINK18"></a><a name="OLE_LINK17"></a>for further cooperation and win the future together.</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:3:"eng";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:12:"picture_urls";s:2:"[]";s:10:"model_name";s:12:"单页模型";s:10:"table_name";s:4:"page";}i:40;a:22:{s:2:"id";s:2:"13";s:4:"name";s:28:"SINO-GERMAN EXPERT CONMITTEE";s:5:"ename";s:9:"conmittee";s:7:"cat_pic";s:0:"";s:3:"pid";s:1:"0";s:8:"model_id";s:1:"2";s:4:"type";s:1:"0";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:120:"Sino-German Industrial Design Center is responsible for integrating international and domestic design resources and supp";s:17:"template_category";s:0:"";s:13:"template_list";s:20:"List_eventspage.html";s:13:"template_show";s:17:"Show_article.html";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:1:"8";s:3:"des";s:0:"";s:3:"eng";s:0:"";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:12:"picture_urls";s:2:"[]";s:10:"model_name";s:12:"单页模型";s:10:"table_name";s:4:"page";}}